{
"type": "fix",
"subject": "resolve immediately check for already resolved objects",
"body": "The resolveImmediately method now checks if an object is already resolved before attempting to resolve it. This prevents unnecessary log messages and object resolution attempts. The method also logs a message when an object is not persistent and a resolve request is made. The resolve request is also logged when an object is not resolved. The object's resolved state is not set to true in the resolveImmediately method. This is because the object's resolved state is set to true in the resolveImmediately method of the object store."
}

